      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty to believe it. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in stunning, showroom-ready shape. It looks and drives just like it did the day it was first bought! There isn't a single blemish to be found\u2014it's truly a gem. I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take a look!",
