    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine E46 M3, a quintessential driver\u2019s machine featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This specimen boasts a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and the factory variable M differential lock. Mechanically flawless, the VANOS system has been overhauled, and the rod bearings have been replaced as preventative maintenance. The chassis remains rigid with zero subframe fatigue. Finished in concours-level paint with an immaculate interior, this car delivers an analog steering feel and linear power delivery that modern vehicles simply cannot replicate.",
