    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this vehicle is the pinnacle of meticulous ownership. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with a professional ceramic coating applied just six months ago; there are absolutely no stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state. The premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, the original floor mats are pristine, and it has never been smoked in or seen a drop of rain. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It comes with a binder of every service record from day one, including a proactive major service performed last month. All four tires are brand-new Michelin Pilot Sport 4S. It has been exclusively garage-kept under a soft cover and driven only on fair-weather weekends. This is quite simply the finest example currently on the market, ready for a collector or a discerning driver who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
